In the FEM, symmetry properties can be applied to
โข Reduce the size of the problems and thus save CPU time, disk space, post-processing efforts, and so on
โข Simplify the modeling task
โข Check the FEM results (make sure the results are symmetrical if the geometry and loading of the structure are symmetrical)
Symmetry properties of a structure should be fully exploited and retained in the FE model to ensure the efficiency and quality of FE solutions.

